$NetBSD: patch-lp__solve_ccc,v 1.6 2024/07/02 12:00:17 tnn Exp $

recent versions of gcc are noisy unless main() is declared returning 'int'
and isnan() needs a floating argument else NOISNAN is defined causing
problems.

